# Allowlist policy: ignore EVERYTHING, then re-admit only our own source and
# documentation. This directory also holds a 7.8 GB disc image, ~36 GB of
# extracted game assets and several hundred MB of third-party tools, none of
# which belong in a repository — an allowlist means none of it can be added by
# accident, even by `git add -A`.

*

# --- our code ---
!tools/
!tools/**/*.py
!tools/**/*.java
!nhl2k10_extractor_gui.py
!run_ghidra_headless.bat

# --- documentation ---
!docs/
!docs/*.md
!docs/*.csv
!README.md
!LICENSE
!requirements.txt
!.gitignore

# --- never, under any circumstances ---
# Game data: you supply your own legally obtained disc.
*.iso
*.iso.undo.json
*.xex
*.xma
*.bnk
*.dds
*.wav
extracted/
2k10*iso*extract*result/
isoextract/
preview/

# Decompiler output derived from the retail executable — see README.
docs/ghidra_decompiled.c

# Third-party tools: install these yourself, they are not ours to redistribute.
ghidra_*/
jdk/
QuickBMS/
Noesis/
iso2god-*/
20209.3_Xenon_Recovery_with_Symbols/
2K BMS Scripts*/

# --- junk ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.log
.venv/
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
